text: The Gohel Koli (also spelled as Gohil Koli) is a clan (Gotra, Kutumb) of the Koli caste mostly found in the Indian state of Gujarat and Union Territory of Daman and Diu and nearby. Gohel Kolis drived their name from the Gohelwar region of Saurashtra in Gujarat. == References == Category:Koli clans
title: Gohel Koli
